.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-NETWORK-INFO" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-network-info \- show node identity and network addresses
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-network-info
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the node's public key, alias, colour, announced addresses,
local bindings, peer count, and active channel count from
.BR getinfo .
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{id, alias, color, addresses, bindings,
 num_peers, num_active_channels}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-version (1),
.BR lightning-node-health (1)
